      "comment": "FRENZY (7) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (31.44) in a Grade 5 at The Meadows. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Can make amends. MOTORSPORT (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at The Meadows behind Paw Xantippe (30.49) in a Grade 5. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Can measure up. ANGRY MURRAY COD (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at Healesville over 350m behind Avengement (19.82) in a Grade 5 FIN. Placed at his previous run. The form out of last race has been strong. One of the main contenders. GAS LANTERN (4) has strong credentials from this draw.",
